scripts.name: Untitled
scripts.script:
end
:touch
scroll "Why, a customer!"
scroll "What advice would you like?"
scroll ""
scroll "Good advice: 5 gems" good
scroll "Bad advice:  1 gem" bad
scroll "Test 1: gt 1 gem" test1
scroll "Test 2: gte 1 gem" test2
scroll "Test 3: lt 1 gem" test3
scroll "Test 4: lte 1 gem" test4
scroll "Test 5: eq 1 gem" test5
scroll "Test 6: not eq 1 gem" test6
scroll "Set 5 blahs" test7
scroll "No advice:   free" none
end
:good
lock
take 5 gems toopoor
scroll "\"A fool and his money"
scroll "  are soon parted...\""
unlock
end
:bad
lock
take 1 gems toopoor
scroll "Buy CDs."
unlock
end
:none
lock
scroll "If you insist..."
scroll "But please take this ammo."
give 1000 ammo
send zombie touch
send catchphrase
end
:toopoor
lock
scroll "You don't have enough gems."
unlock
end
:test1
if gems gt 1 ok
scroll "Not met!"
end
:test2
if gems gte 1 ok
scroll "Not met!"
end
:test3
if gems lt 1 ok
scroll "Not met!"
end
:test4
if gems lte 1 ok
scroll "Not met!"
end
:test5
if gems eq 1 ok
scroll "Not met!"
end
:test6
if not gems eq 1 ok
scroll "Not met!"
end
:test7
set 5 blahs
say "OK. Done."
end
:ok
scroll "all is well!"
end
:catchphrase
scroll "And that's the end of that chapter!"
unlock
end

:loop
if aligned north shootnorth
if aligned e shooteast
if aligned s shootsouth
if aligned w shootwest
send loop
:shootnorth

send loop
:shooteast
shoot east
send loop
:shootsouth
shoot south
send loop
:shootwest
shoot west
send loop
:touch
if adjacent n greetn
if adjacent e greete
if adjacent s greets
if adjacent w greetw
send continue
end
:greetn
say "Northbound visitor!"
send continue
:greete
say "Eastbound visitor!"
send continue
:greets
say "Southbound visitor!"
send continue
:greetw
say "Westbound visitor!"
:continue
go smart 1000
end
:shot

:shot
zap shot
char 2
char 1
end

die
end

die
